"title": "8796: persecution, forms of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8796",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture identifies a number of reasons why individuals and governmments may attempt to persecute believers and also the methods by which they may carry this out.</p>\n<h2>The motives for persecution</h2>\n<h3>Envy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:17-Acts5:18\">ACT 5:17–5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:14-Gen26:15\">GEN 26:14–26:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:4\">GEN 37:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:8\">GEN 37:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:8-1Sam18:9\">1SA 18:8–18:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:16\">PSA 106:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:1-Dan6:5\">DAN 6:1–6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:18\">MAT 27:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:45\">ACT 13:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:16\">JAS 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>Fear</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:2\">LUK 22:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:10\">EXO 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:15\">1SA 18:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:29\">1SA 18:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:3\">MAT 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:23-Acts19:27\">ACT 19:23–19:27</a></p>\n<h3>Hatred</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:12\">1JN 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:3-Gen4:8\">GEN 4:3–4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:8\">1KI 22:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:7\">2CH 18:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:7\">JHN 7:7</a></p>\n<h2>The means of persecution</h2>\n<h3>Deception</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:12\">PSA 38:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:10\">1KI 21:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:12-Ezra4:13\">EZR 4:12–4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:11\">PSA 35:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:10\">JER 20:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos7:10\">AMO 7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:11\">MAT 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:12\">JHN 7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:11\">ACT 6:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:21\">ACT 21:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:28\">ACT 21:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:5\">ACT 24:5</a></p>\n<h3>Threats</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:7\">PSA 10:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:4\">EZR 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:15\">DAN 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:22\">JHN 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:17\">ACT 4:17</a></p>\n<h3>Ridicule</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:1-Neh4:3\">NEH 4:1–4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:7\">HOS 9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:13\">1CO 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:13\">HEB 13:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:9\">REV 2:9</a></p>\n<h3>Ostracism</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:22\">MAT 10:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:29\">JHN 9:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:34\">JHN 9:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:42\">JHN 12:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:2\">JHN 16:2</a></p>\n<h3>Violence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:35\">ROM 8:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:6\">JER 38:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:17\">MAT 10:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:9\">MRK 13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:18-John21:19\">JHN 21:18–21:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:40\">ACT 5:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:37\">ACT 16:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:25\">2CO 11:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:17\">GAL 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:36-Heb11:39\">HEB 11:36–11:39</a></p>\n<h2>How God deals with persecutors</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:13\">1TI 1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:34-Dan4:35\">DAN 4:34–4:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:1\">ACT 12:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:21-Acts12:23\">ACT 12:21–12:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:23\">GAL 1:23</a></p>",
